msgctxt "an6.117:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 12. Sāmaññavagga → vaggāsaṅgahitā suttantā (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an6.117:0.2"
msgid "12. Sāmaññavagga "
msgstr "12. The Ascetic Life "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.117:0.3"
msgid "117. Kāyānupassīsutta "
msgstr "117. Observing the Body "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an6.117:1.1"
msgid "“Cha, bhikkhave, dhamme appahāya abhabbo kāye kāyānupassī viharituṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, without giving up these six qualities you can’t meditate observing an aspect of the body. "

msgctxt "an6.117:1.2"
msgid "Katame cha? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.117:1.3"
msgid "Kammārāmataṃ, bhassārāmataṃ, niddārāmataṃ, saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ, indriyesu aguttadvārataṃ, bhojane amattaññutaṃ. "
msgstr "Relishing work, talk, sleep, and company, not guarding the sense doors, and eating too much. "

msgctxt "an6.117:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhamme appahāya abhabbo kāye kāyānupassī viharituṃ. "
msgstr "Without giving up these six qualities you can’t meditate observing an aspect of the body. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.450, sc2
msgctxt "an6.117:2.1"
msgid "Cha, bhikkhave, dhamme pahāya bhabbo kāye kāyānupassī viharituṃ. "
msgstr "But after giving up these six qualities you can meditate observing an aspect of the body. "

msgctxt "an6.117:2.2"
msgid "Katame cha? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.117:2.3"
msgid "Kammārāmataṃ, bhassārāmataṃ, niddārāmataṃ, saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ, indriyesu aguttadvārataṃ, bhojane amattaññutaṃ. "
msgstr "Relishing work, talk, sleep, and company, not guarding the sense doors, and eating too much. "

msgctxt "an6.117:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhamme pahāya bhabbo kāye kāyānupassī viharitun”ti. "
msgstr "After giving up these six qualities you can meditate observing an aspect of the body.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.117:2.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

